HEADWORD: Gargantuan
<hw>Gar*gan"tu*an</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<ets>Gargantua</ets>, an allegorical hero of Rabelais.]</ety>
<def>Characteristic of Gargantua, a gigantic, wonderful personage;
enormous; prodigious; inordinate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

